<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Invitación Dama de Honor</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --verde-principal: #2f5d50;
  --verde-oscuro: #1e3d35;
  --verde-suave: #e8f3ef;
  --blanco: #ffffff;
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
  background: var(--verde-suave);
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  overflow:hidden;
}

/* SOBRE */
.wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 400px;
  height: 260px;
  cursor: pointer;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 14px;
  background: var(--verde-principal);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  transition: opacity 1s ease;
  z-index: 5;
}

.flap {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--verde-oscuro);
  clip-path: polygon(0 0, 50% 60%, 100% 0);
  transform-origin: top;
  transition: transform 1s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
  z-index: 10;
  border-radius: 14px 14px 0 0;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

/* CARTA */
.letter {
  position: absolute;
  width: 400px; /* más grande */
  max-width: 90vw;
  height: auto;
  background: var(--blanco);
  border-radius: 14px;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, 50%) scale(0.7); /* empieza pequeña y baja */
  padding: 40px;
  text-align: center;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: all 1s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
  z-index: 20;
  pointer-events: none;
  box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
}

.letter h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  color: var(--verde-principal);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.letter p {
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--verde-oscuro);
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.question {
  font-size: 24px;
  margin: 20px 0;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.buttons {
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.8s ease;
}

button {
  padding: 14px 28px;
  margin: 10px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-size: 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
  border: none;
}

.btn-si {
  background: var(--verde-principal);
  color: white;
}

.btn-si:hover { background: var(--verde-oscuro); }

.btn-abrazo {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid var(--verde-principal);
  color: var(--verde-principal);
}

.btn-abrazo:hover { background: var(--verde-suave); }

/* Animaciones */
.scene.open .flap { transform: rotateX(180deg); box-shadow: none; }

.scene.open .letter {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); /* carta centrada y grande */
  pointer-events: auto;
}

.scene.open .buttons {
  opacity: 1;
  transition-delay: 0.6s;
}

.scene.open .wrapper {
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 480px){
  .letter { width: 280px; padding: 30px; }
  .letter h1 { font-size: 24px; }
  .letter p { font-size: 16px; }
  .question { font-size: 20px; }
  button { font-size: 14px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scene" id="scene">

  <div class="wrapper" id="wrapper" onclick="openEnvelope()">
    <div class="flap"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="letter" id="letter">
    <h1>Daniela Marín</h1>
    <p>Desde el momento en que imaginé este día, supe que quería a mi lado a alguien que ha sido parte esencial de mi historia.</p>
    <p>Y esa persona eres tú.</p>
    <div class="question">¿Aceptarías ser mi dama de honor? 💚</div>
    <div class="buttons">
      <button class="btn-si" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); alert('¡Sabía que dirías que sí! 💚');">Sí, acepto</button>
      <button class="btn-abrazo" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); alert('Abrazo infinito primero 🤍');">Necesito un abrazo</button>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
function openEnvelope() {
  const scene = document.getElementById('scene');
  if (!scene.classList.contains('open')) {
    scene.classList.add('open');
  }
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
